      "description": "CFD-predicted hemolysis index values compared against in-vitro measurements from the FDA generic centrifugal pump test rig at five flow-speed operating points. Agreement within 18% at four of five points; outlier at low-flow high-speed condition attributed to cavitation onset not captured by the turbulence model.",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/synth/activity/bench-validation-campaign-2023",
      "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cfd-predicts-absolute-hemolysis-vad-cou2"
